  "title": "KITCHEN ASSISTANT",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities including but not limited to:</strong><br /></p><ul><li>Involved in the preparation of food and beverages</li><li>Ensure that kitchen utensils and equipment are in good condition to operate</li><li>Responsible for maintenance of cleanliness of kitchen and any ad-hoc duties assigned</li><li>Ensure compliance with all health and safety regulations in a kitchen area</li><li>Ensure that food can be prepared in a timely manner</li><li>Ability to work in a fast-paced environment</li><li>Ensure freshness of food items and discard expired/ spoilt items</li><li>Observe food stock levels and place orders when necessary</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>No experience required as on-the-job training will be provided</li><li>Pleasant disposition and well-groomed</li><li>At least a Certificate in Food & Beverage service</li><li>Able to commit shift work, weekends and public holidays</li></ul>",
